---
title: New England-Style Salmon Rolls with Apple Salad
description: Inspired by New England's famous lobster rolls, this salmon packs a similar creamy, zesty, lemon-pepper punch (without the trip across the border!). A crisp apple salad alongside adds fresh, tart sweetness.

